text: São Roque de Minas is an Brazilian municipality in the state of Minas Gerais. In 2020, 7,076 people lived there and its area is 2,100 km².IBGE 2020 These municipalities next to São Roque de Minas are: Medeiros (N), Bambuí (E), Piumhi (SE), Vargem Bonita and Delfinópolis (S), Conquista and Tapira (W). == References == Category:Municipalities in Minas Gerais
title: São Roque de Minas
